snippet.title: BANG BANG BANG [beatmania ClubMIX, 5keys, Arcade]
snippet.description:
First arcade ClubMIX video (here, on Youtube, and elsewhere probably). Not that it matters...

Not much to add, except this song is catchy and that stick figure dancing on the tooth is awesome, and you shouldn't play it at Hi Speed 3 (oops).

I've experimented with a different camera angle here - the camera is lower, I'm playing on the left instead of the right, and it's a more distant view which means you can see a bit of the top and the sides too - yeah, this is a mini cab.
